- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a model for managing distributed resources in a distribution network, which involves control and optimization of the system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed model may involve the use of AI techniques for optimization and decision-making. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper deals with the management of distributed resources in a network, which may involve distributed computing and communication. 
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies): The paper deals with the emerging trend of microgrids and distributed energy resources, and proposes a new entity (DMO) to manage them. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve the development of software tools and platforms for implementing the proposed model and managing the distributed resources.
